data.description: As you enter the large foyer with a closet you will appreciate this spacious home on over a half acre with a full basement. This 3 bed 2 bath could be a 5 bed 3 bath home with some finishing in the basement. This is not your average split level home, it has vaulted ceilings, beautiful oak floors, solid oak 6 panel doors throughout, new roof, stainless steel Frigidaire appliances, large yard and a great location!
